comment:
* The request object wrapping the required and optional parameters to schedule a deferred update
 * for Custom Audience on device. Allows AdTechs to provide an Update Uri, and the minimum Delay
 * Time to schedule the update.

methods.name: public Uri getUpdateUri()
methods.comment: Returns the {@link Uri} from which the Custom Audience is to be fetched

methods.name: public Duration getMinDelay()
methods.comment: Returns the {@link Duration} min time duration for which the update is deferred

methods.name: public List<PartialCustomAudience> getPartialCustomAudienceList()
methods.comment:
* Returns the list of {@link PartialCustomAudience} which are sent along with the request to
     * download the update for Custom Audience

methods.name: public int hashCode()
methods.comment: Returns the hash of {@link ScheduleCustomAudienceUpdateRequest} object's data.

methods.name: public boolean equals(Object o)
methods.comment:
* @return {@code true} only if two {@link ScheduleCustomAudienceUpdateRequest} objects contain
     *     the same information.
